description: The Sugar Philly Truck wants to spread the sweetness and make it accessible to all those who crave tasty treats, so they are bringing Philly a little piece of heaven. They're satisfying one sweet tooth at time, so keep a look out!The PresentSometimes you just need to treat yourself to something nice. At Sugar Philly, "sometimes" is all the time! You've got classes to attend, meetings to sit in, and piles of work to sift through. You are working hard (or at least trying to), so who better than you to deserve a reward! And Sugar Philly completely agrees! So they climbed the rainbow, snuck into heaven, and brought back some sweets sure to make you smile. Where else can you get this good stuff this easy? Come eat, get a treat, and smile!
name: Sugar Philly
